Wobbly Ride wrote:
#    That's true.  However, in order to read data from a DVD, you 
#    must first "authenticate" to the DVD player.  This is before 
#    any decryption takes place.  This is a cryptographic handshake 
#    mechanism using a key. If you do not perform this handshake, 
#    it is not possible to read the data.

